import React from 'react'
import { Box } from '@mui/system'
import { Drawer, List, ListItemButton, Typography } from '@mui/material'

const Sidebar = () => {
  return (
    <Drawer
        container={window.document.body}
        valiant="permanent"
        open={true}
        sx={{width: 350, height: "100vh"}}
    >
        <List>
            <ListItemButton>
                <Box>
                    <Typography>
                        istone
                    </Typography>
                </Box>
            </ListItemButton>
        </List>
    </Drawer>
  )
}

export default Sidebar
